<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Appointment Confirmed - TechTrainers</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe
      UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #292524; margin: 0;
      padding: 0; background-color: #fafaf9; } .container { max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow:
      hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } .header { background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, #16a34a 0%, #15803d 100%); color: white; padding:
      30px; text-align: center; } .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700; } .header p { margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 16px;
      opacity: 0.9; } .content { padding: 30px; } .appointment-card {
      background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; } .appointment-detail { display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #dcfce7; } .appointment-detail:last-child {
      border-bottom: none; margin-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; } .detail-label
      { font-weight: 600; color: #065f46; min-width: 120px; } .detail-value {
      color: #1e293b; font-weight: 500; } .trainer-info { background: #fef3c7;
      border: 1px solid #fcd34d; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px
      0; } .trainer-info h3 { margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #92400e; font-size:
      16px; } .action-buttons { text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; } .btn {
      display: inline-block; padding: 12px 30px; margin: 0 10px; border-radius:
      6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; transition:
      all 0.3s ease; } .btn-primary { background: #16a34a; color: white; }
      .btn-secondary { background: #6b7280; color: white; } .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); }
      .footer { background: #292524; color: #a8a29e; padding: 20px; text-align:
      center; font-size: 14px; } .footer a { color: #d97706; text-decoration:
      none; } .footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; } .divider { height:
      1px; background: #e2e8f0; margin: 20px 0; } .success-badge { background:
      #dcfce7; color: #166534; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px;
      font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px; } .calendar-attachment { background: #f1f5f9;
      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px
      0; text-align: center; } @media (max-width: 600px) { .container { margin:
      0; border-radius: 0; } .content { padding: 20px; } .header { padding:
      20px; } .btn { display: block; margin: 10px 0; } }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>‚úÖ Appointment Confirmed!</h1>
        <p>Your training session is all set</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi <strong>{{clientName}}</strong>,</p>

        <p>Great news! Your appointment has been confirmed. We're excited to
          help you achieve your fitness goals! üéØ</p>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
          <span class="success-badge">‚úì Confirmed</span>
        </div>

        <div class="appointment-card">
          <div class="appointment-detail">
            <span class="detail-label">üìÖ Date:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentDate}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="appointment-detail">
            <span class="detail-label">‚è∞ Time:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentTime}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="appointment-detail">
            <span class="detail-label">üí™ Session Type:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{sessionType}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="appointment-detail">
            <span class="detail-label">‚è±Ô∏è Duration:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{duration}} minutes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="appointment-detail">
            <span class="detail-label">üìç Location:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{location}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="appointment-detail">
            <span class="detail-label">üè∑Ô∏è Booking ID:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{bookingId}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="trainer-info">
          <h3>üèãÔ∏è Your Personal Trainer</h3>
          <div class="appointment-detail">
            <span class="detail-label">Name:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{trainerName}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="appointment-detail">
            <span class="detail-label">Specialization:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{trainerSpecialization}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="appointment-detail">
            <span class="detail-label">Experience:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{trainerExperience}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="appointment-detail">
            <span class="detail-label">Contact:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{trainerEmail}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="calendar-attachment">
          <p><strong>üìÖ Add to Calendar</strong></p>
          <p>A calendar invitation has been attached to this email. Click to add
            this appointment to your calendar.</p>
          <small>Compatible with Google Calendar, Outlook, Apple Calendar, and
            more.</small>
        </div>

        <div class="action-buttons">
          <a href="{{viewAppointmentUrl}}" class="btn btn-primary">üì± View in
            App</a>
          <a href="{{rescheduleUrl}}" class="btn btn-secondary">üìÖ Reschedule</a>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p><strong>üìù What to Bring:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Comfortable workout clothes</li>
          <li>Water bottle</li>
          <li>Towel</li>
          <li>Any specific equipment mentioned by your trainer</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>‚è∞ Important Reminders:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Please arrive 5-10 minutes early</li>
          <li>Contact us if you need to reschedule (at least 24 hours notice)</li>
          <li>Bring a positive attitude and be ready to work hard! üí™</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p>If you have any questions or need to make changes, don't hesitate to
          contact us at
          <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>
          or visit our
          <a href="{{supportUrl}}">Support Center</a>.</p>

        <p>We're here to support you on your fitness journey!</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br />
          <strong>The TechTrainers Team</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          <strong>TechTrainers</strong>
          - Empowering Fitness Through Technology<br />
          <a href="{{companyWebsite}}">{{companyWebsite}}</a>
          |
          <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a><br />
          <a href="{{manageAppointmentsUrl}}">Manage Appointments</a>
          |
          <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>